}}'''茉莉酸'''，是一種在包括[[茉莉花|茉莉]]的多種植物中所發現的[[有機化合物|有機化合物]]。此化合物屬於[[植物激素|植物激素]]中的[[茉莉酮酸|茉莉酮酸類]]。茉莉酸首次在1957年時被瑞士化學家 Edouard Demole和他的同事由[[茉莉酸甲酯|茉莉酸的甲基酯化形式]]分離得來。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Isolement et determination de la structure du jasmonate de methyle, constituent odorant characteristique de l'essence de jasmin|first1=E.|last2=Lederer|first2=E.|date=1962|journal=Helvetica Chimica Acta|doi=10.1002/hlca.19620450233|volume=45|pages=675–685|language=fr|trans-title=Isolation and determination of the structure of methyl jasmonate, the aromatic constituent [that is] characteristic of the essential oil of jasmine|last3=Mercier|first3=D.|last1=Demole}}{{cite journal|title=The chemistry and creative legacy of methyl jasmonate and hedione|url=https://perfumerflavorist.texterity.com/perfumerflavorist/201112?pg=40#pg40|first1=Christian|date=December 2011|journal=Perfumer & Flavorist|volume=36|pages=36–48|last1=Chapuis|access-date=2021-09-09|archive-date=2021-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211127205651/https://perfumerflavorist.texterity.com/perfumerflavorist/201112?pg=40#pg40|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 衍生物 ==
{{Main|茉莉酮酸}}
茉莉酸可被轉換為其各式衍生物，包括其甲基酯型態的[[茉莉酸甲酯|茉莉酸甲酯]]。此轉換可由茉莉酸羧基甲基轉移酶[[催化|催化]]<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Jasmonic acid carboxyl methyltransferase: a key enzyme for jasmonate-regulated plant responses|first1=H. S.|last2=Song|first2=J. T.|date=2001-04-10|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America|issue=8|doi=10.1073/pnas.081557298|volume=98|pages=4788–4793|bibcode=2001PNAS...98.4788S|issn=0027-8424|pmc=31912|pmid=11287667|last3=Cheong|first3=J. J.|last4=Lee|first4=Y. H.|last5=Lee|first5=Y. W.|last6=Hwang|first6=I.|last7=Lee|first7=J. S.|last8=Choi|first8=Y. D.|last1=Seo|doi-access=free}}</ref>。在生物體內也可以異構為[[胺基酸|胺基酸]]。茉莉酸的[[脫羧反應|去羧化]]可產生具芳香味的[[茉莉酮|茉莉酮]]。

